entries.femaleVariant: Good work, kid. You keep it up, could make shift lead.
Nah, not for me. Soon as I save up enough, I'm goin' to college.
College? Eh, come on. Whaddaya need college for? Only thing you'll get is a mountain of debt.
Yeah. And a decent corp job.
Pssh. You think all you need is a diploma, and suddenly it's raining eddies? Not in this world, son.
